{"tid":56912,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大帽山就快跌破零度，有無人去睇落雪","createTime":"2016-12-27T15:17:23.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-28T02:11:02.000Z","uid":14918,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dcc9903dd3dfdc53aed377c312218ab9abd7a9c5","tid":56912,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T15:17:23.000Z","msg":"有無on9去睇落雪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/27/231720_5b5a284186f9be6bafae16206290ee63.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F27%2F231720_5b5a284186f9be6bafae16206290ee63.jpg&h=a837a87c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c7de883be20e8a3bf112b6ccf5e9636364cea7bc","tid":56912,"uid":29523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T15:19:31.000Z","msg":"仲好熱<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a71a0e3c904c0e61114d540eb59b2ea6c685c48","tid":56912,"uid":9677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T16:29:06.000Z","msg":"又等消防員救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59eda9283dd9a3853fa0670d6e89d352f9a649f4","tid":56912,"uid":67201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T16:36:45.000Z","msg":"十五度，西班牙人穿大衣、戴手套；西伯利亞人作日光浴。<br />\n十度，法國人開暖氣；西伯利亞人在花園裡種花。<br />\n五度，義大利人發不動車子，西伯利亞人開敞篷車遊街。<br />\n零下五度，加州人凍斃了；西伯利亞人在戶外烤肉。<br />\n零下十度，英國人開暖氣；西伯利亞人開始穿長袖。<br />\n零下五十度，北極熊撤離北極；西伯利亞軍隊延後冬季野外求生訓練，等待真正的冬天到來。<br />\n零下一百八十三度，食物中的微生物死亡；西伯利亞牛隻抱怨酪農的手太冰。<br />\n零下兩百七十三度，原子停止活動；西伯利亞人終於說：『老天，外面好冷！』<br />\n高登仔：『最近天氣開始轉涼了！』<br />\n連登仔 :  『好撚熱呀屌！』"},{"pid":"11eb7f5ca66b2584a86f147713126db30394731e","tid":56912,"uid":6222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T16:40:05.000Z","msg":"想睇班柒頭要等待救援<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee41f4fb877b6fa6b0fe90e6b37ca15fbd537acf","tid":56912,"uid":17075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T16:42:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想睇班柒頭要等待救援<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一陣搞到救援隊都整親先最仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e39611cdcc74c9d56245b07df176caa0d7da4a1f","tid":56912,"uid":13149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T18:04:20.000Z","msg":"留名睇有傻西上山話條命我自己既"},{"pid":"350e78ff715cf3f8a70516108b014e12553827ab","tid":56912,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T23:11:10.000Z","msg":"2.4<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本身以為0.2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dce200765bde7882dbefb4ca096f75674220ca2e","tid":56912,"uid":29201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T23:18:52.000Z","msg":"諗起上年成班on9上山睇結霜加仆街"},{"pid":"c2dd82b7d0f92a73350c94ffebc83dc61e78b375","tid":56912,"uid":17776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T23:22:25.000Z","msg":"上去玩Mario賽車<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02436ce547541d18b8a3f497892273e95a966e2a","tid":56912,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T23:24:01.000Z","msg":"一車車港豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27e12d4f9a854f49eea868a5e513c7bd69259116","tid":56912,"uid":2757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T23:24:59.000Z","msg":"條命係我嘅，唔關你事<br />\n救人係你嘅責任，你要負責<br />\n<br />\n即係點啫...<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87d3a097a33c2b8ae836560a58ac7de4286343db","tid":56912,"uid":56993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T23:30:19.000Z","msg":"Non sense<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbfe460d3dba8d59c52a49d2a8b